<div class="row">
  <div class="small-centered columns center-text">
    <h1 class="center-text">SpotCheck</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="small-2 columns">
    <%= image_tag("spotcheck_logo_dark.png", alt: "SpotCheck logo") %>
  </div>
  <div class="small-10 columns">
    <h4>SpotCheck is a repository for your creative video projects, housing revisions, comments, and changes under one roof.</h3>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="small-centered columns center-text">
    <%= video_tag("spotcheck_demo.mp4", controls: true, size: "640x360", poster: 'spotcheck_poster.png') %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row top-padding">
  <div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-centered columns center-text">
        <i class="fi-play-video"></i>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h5 class="center-text">Are You a Creator?</h5>
    <p>As a content creator, post your work when it's ready to be reviewed by clients. Be notified when clients have comments.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-centered columns center-text">
        <i class="fi-pencil"></i>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h5 class="center-text">Are You a Producer?</h5>
    <p>While collaborating with a creative professional, you can view each revision and request changes.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-centered columns center-text">
        <i class="fi-clock"></i>
      </div>
    </div>
  <h5 class="center-text">Is your time valuable?</h5>
  <p>Stop wasting time digging through email threads to check the status of a project. Check for approval instantly.</p>
  </div>
</div>
